						<div class="postbody">Apparently you can't even get in gameplay with this hack.<br /><br />I think it should be hard to go with MMC5 -&gt; MMC3, especially because of PRG bankswitching which is 8k, 8k, 16k on MMC3, but 16k, 8k, 8k on VRC6 and the MMC5 mode that is used by CV3.<br /><br />If this would have been possible, Konami would have done it really. It would have saved them much costs.</div>

